snippet.title: HUGE WIN For Johnny Depp in Court! Amber faces multiple felony charges!
snippet.description:
New information has occurred in the Johnny Depp vs. Amber Heard case and I wanted to bring you the latest updates! 

Amber Heard has tried to use Anti-Slapp laws to get the case thrown out but the judge did not buy it. 

Amber Heard also faces multiple felony charges if she loses the defamation lawsuit. The ACLU and Amber are frantically trying to get the case thrown out but Johnny Depp's lawyer Adam Waldman calls this "her last Hail Mary."

Other sources and videos for this information

Come Geek Some Channel - https://youtu.be/CLDFWBnWkPE
That Umbrella Guy Channel - https://youtu.be/dOEUc4LEQMI

My other videos on this situation:

Johnny Depp and Amber Heard: The Complete Story - https://youtu.be/CMxp-tlyQrw

Johnny Depp Vs. Amber Heard: The Complete Story part 2 - https://youtu.be/JsMEJhMjTGA

BOMBSHELL NEWS: The ACLU planned all this with Amber Heard - https://youtu.be/--Te2eW6viU

My Equipment:

The video footage was shot using a Canon EOS M50 Mark 2
My microphone is a Blue Yeticaster professional broadcast bundle. With yeti USB microphone, Radius 3 shockmount, and Compass Boom Arm
The lighting I use is a GVM bicolor LED video light
The video editing program I use is Cyberlink Powerdirector 365 version 19
